
🧙Harry Potter, also known as The Boy Who Lived. My journey began at 4 Privet Drive, but his true home is at Hogwarts School of Witchcraft and Wizardry. he is  best known for his battle against Lord Voldemort, my time as a Gryffindor Seeker, and his close friendship with Hermione Granger and Ron Weasley.

⚡ Abilities & Skills

Proficient in Defensive Magic 🛡️

Skilled in Patronus Charm (Expecto Patronum) ✨

Experienced in Dueling & Combat Magic 🏹

Fluent in Parseltongue (formerly) 🐍

Expert in Breaking School Rules (with good intentions) 📜


📜 Notable Achievements

Defeated Lord Voldemort and ended the Second Wizarding War 🏆

Won the Triwizard Tournament (sort of) 🏅

Member of Dumbledore’s Army and fought in the Battle of Hogwarts ⚔️

Youngest Quidditch Seeker in a century 🏆


